Yeah, we'll send you a tape of the finished product. I'll probably write it up pretty quick,

28:11.560 --> 28:14.720
and we'll get a few shows out of it, and we'll send it on to you. Yeah.

28:14.840 --> 28:19.960
When you send that to me, could you also like to go to the list of the stations we'll be

28:19.960 --> 28:23.760
broadcast, because I know the public relations people at Simon Schuster would like to know that.

28:23.760 --> 28:27.300
Sure. Be glad to. Okay. No problem. George, thanks again.

28:27.640 --> 28:29.880
Keep on writing. Look forward to seeing what's coming out next.

28:30.300 --> 28:32.180
Sounds good. I'll see you at Texas Con.

28:32.380 --> 28:33.400
Great. Bye-bye now.

